query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 tq1 s) NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoMergeJoin(acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 1 AND q1.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('algebra-precalculus',
'arithmetic',
'category-theory',
'contest-math',
'differential-geometry',
'diophantine-equations',
'linear-algebra',
'numerical-methods',
'stochastic-processes',
'vectors')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Civic Duty',
'Critic',
'Custodian',
'Enthusiast',
'Explainer',
'Good Answer',
'Informed',
'Necromancer',
'Nice Answer',
'Notable Question',
'Organizer',
'Revival',
'Student',
'Supporter',
'Yearling') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
